#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.159"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.159:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.159:0.2"
msgid "16. Indriyavagga"
msgstr "16. Faculties"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.159:0.3"
msgid "159. Bhikkhunīsutta"
msgstr "159. Nun"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.145"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. <span class="evam">
msgctxt "an4.159:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

#. </span>
msgctxt "an4.159:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā ānando kosambiyaṃ viharati ghositārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time Venerable Ānanda was staying near Kosambi, in Ghosita’s "
"Monastery."

msgctxt "an4.159:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho aññatarā bhikkhunī aññataraṃ purisaṃ āmantesi:"
msgstr "And then a certain nun addressed a man:"

msgctxt "an4.159:1.4"
msgid ""
"“ehi tvaṃ, ambho purisa, yenayyo ānando tenupasaṅkama; upasaṅkamitvā mama "
"vacanena ayyassa ānandassa pāde sirasā vanda:"
msgstr ""
"“Please, mister, go to Venerable Ānanda, and in my name bow with your head "
"to his feet. Say to him:"

msgctxt "an4.159:1.5"
msgid "‘itthannāmā, bhante, bhikkhunī ābādhikinī dukkhitā bāḷhagilānā."
msgstr "‘Sir, the nun named so-and-so is sick, suffering, and gravely ill."

msgctxt "an4.159:1.6"
msgid "Sā ayyassa ānandassa pāde sirasā vandatī’ti. Evañca vadehi:"
msgstr "She bows with her head to your feet.’ And then say:"

msgctxt "an4.159:1.7"
msgid ""
"‘sādhu kira, bhante, ayyo ānando yena bhikkhunupassayo yena sā bhikkhunī "
"tenupasaṅkamatu anukampaṃ upādāyā’”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Sir, please go to the nuns’ quarters to visit that nun out of compassion.’”"

msgctxt "an4.159:1.8"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃ, ayye”ti kho so puriso tassā bhikkhuniyā paṭissutvā yenāyasmā ānando "
"tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ "
"nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so puriso āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "“Yes, ma’am,” that man replied. He did as the nun asked."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.159:2.1"
msgid "“Itthannāmā, bhante, bhikkhunī ābādhikinī dukkhitā bāḷhagilānā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.159:2.2"
msgid "Sā āyasmato ānandassa pāde sirasā vandati, evañca vadeti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.159:2.3"
msgid ""
"‘sādhu kira, bhante, āyasmā ānando yena bhikkhunupassayo yena sā bhikkhunī "
"tenupasaṅkamatu anukampaṃ upādāyā’”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.159:2.4"
msgid "Adhivāsesi kho āyasmā ānando tuṇhībhāvena."
msgstr "Ānanda consented in silence."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.159:3.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya yena bhikkhunupassayo "
"yena sā bhikkhunī tenupasaṅkami."
msgstr ""
"Then Ānanda robed up and went to the nuns’ quarters to visit that nun, "
"taking his bowl and robe."

msgctxt "an4.159:3.2"
msgid "Addasā kho sā bhikkhunī āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ dūratova āgacchantaṃ."
msgstr "That nun saw Ānanda coming off in the distance."

msgctxt "an4.159:3.3"
msgid "Disvā sasīsaṃ pārupitvā mañcake nipajji."
msgstr "She wrapped herself up from head to foot and laid down on her cot."

msgctxt "an4.159:3.4"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena sā bhikkhunī tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"paññatte āsane nisīdi. Nisajja kho āyasmā ānando taṃ bhikkhuniṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Ānanda went up to her, and sat down on the seat spread out. "
"Then Ānanda said to the nun:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.159:4.1"
msgid "“Āhārasambhūto ayaṃ, bhagini, kāyo āhāraṃ nissāya."
msgstr "“Sister, this body is produced by food. Relying on food,"

msgctxt "an4.159:4.2"
msgid "Āhāro pahātabbo."
msgstr "you should give up food."

msgctxt "an4.159:4.3"
msgid "Taṇhāsambhūto ayaṃ, bhagini, kāyo taṇhaṃ nissāya."
msgstr "This body is produced by craving. Relying on craving,"

msgctxt "an4.159:4.4"
msgid "Taṇhā pahātabbā."
msgstr "you should give up craving."

msgctxt "an4.159:4.5"
msgid "Mānasambhūto ayaṃ, bhagini, kāyo mānaṃ nissāya."
msgstr "This body is produced by conceit. Relying on conceit,"

msgctxt "an4.159:4.6"
msgid "Māno pahātabbo."
msgstr "you should give up conceit."

msgctxt "an4.159:4.7"
msgid "Methunasambhūto ayaṃ, bhagini, kāyo."
msgstr "This body is produced by sex."

msgctxt "an4.159:4.8"
msgid "Methune ca setughāto vutto bhagavatā."
msgstr "The Buddha spoke of breaking off everything to do with sex."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.159:5.1"
msgid "‘Āhārasambhūto ayaṃ, bhagini, kāyo āhāraṃ nissāya."
msgstr "‘This body is produced by food. Relying on food,"

msgctxt "an4.159:5.2"
msgid "Āhāro pahātabbo’ti, iti kho panetaṃ vuttaṃ."
msgstr "you should give up food.’ This is what I said,"

msgctxt "an4.159:5.3"
msgid "Kiñcetaṃ paṭicca vuttaṃ?"
msgstr "but why did I say it?"

msgctxt "an4.159:5.4"
msgid "Idha, bhagini, bhikkhu paṭisaṅkhā yoniso āhāraṃ āhāreti:"
msgstr "Take a mendicant who reflects properly on the food that they eat:"

msgctxt "an4.159:5.5"
msgid ""
"‘neva davāya na madāya na maṇḍanāya na vibhūsanāya, yāvadeva imassa kāyassa "
"ṭhitiyā yāpanāya vihiṃsūparatiyā brahmacariyānuggahāya. Iti purāṇañca "
"vedanaṃ paṭihaṅkhāmi, navañca vedanaṃ na uppādessāmi. Yātrā ca me bhavissati "
"anavajjatā ca phāsuvihāro cā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Not for fun, indulgence, adornment, or decoration, but only to continue and "
"sustain this body, avoid harm, and support spiritual practice. To put an end "
"to old discomfort and not give rise to new discomfort. And so that I’ll keep "
"on living blamelessly and at ease.’"

msgctxt "an4.159:5.6"
msgid "So aparena samayena āhāraṃ nissāya āhāraṃ pajahati."
msgstr "After some time, relying on food, they give up food."

msgctxt "an4.159:5.7"
msgid "‘Āhārasambhūto ayaṃ, bhagini, kāyo āhāraṃ nissāya āhāro pahātabbo’t "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.159:5.8"
msgid "iti yaṃ taṃ vuttaṃ idametaṃ paṭicca vuttaṃ."
msgstr "That’s why I said what I said."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.146"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an4.159:6.1"
msgid "‘Taṇhāsambhūto ayaṃ, bhagini, kāyo taṇhaṃ nissāya."
msgstr "‘This body is produced by craving. Relying on craving,"

msgctxt "an4.159:6.2"
msgid "Taṇhā pahātabbā’ti, iti kho panetaṃ vuttaṃ."
msgstr "you should give up craving.’ This is what I said,"

msgctxt "an4.159:6.3"
msgid "Kiñcetaṃ paṭicca vuttaṃ?"
msgstr "but why did I say it?"

msgctxt "an4.159:6.4"
msgid "Idha, bhagini, bhikkhu suṇāti:"
msgstr "Take a mendicant who hears this:"

msgctxt "an4.159:6.5"
msgid ""
"‘itthannāmo kira bhikkhu āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ "
"diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘They say that the mendicant named so-and-so has realized the undefiled "
"freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in this very life. And they live "
"having realized it with their own insight due to the ending of defilements.’"

msgctxt "an4.159:6.6"
msgid "Tassa evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "They think:"

msgctxt "an4.159:6.7"
msgid ""
"‘kudāssu nāma ahampi āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ "
"diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharissāmī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Oh, when will I too realize the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by "
"wisdom in this very life. …’"

msgctxt "an4.159:6.8"
msgid "So aparena samayena taṇhaṃ nissāya taṇhaṃ pajahati."
msgstr "After some time, relying on craving, they give up craving."

msgctxt "an4.159:6.9"
msgid "‘Taṇhāsambhūto ayaṃ, bhagini, kāyo taṇhaṃ nissāya taṇhā pahātabbā’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.159:6.10"
msgid "iti yaṃ taṃ vuttaṃ idametaṃ paṭicca vuttaṃ."
msgstr "That's why I said what I said."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an4.159:7.1"
msgid "‘Mānasambhūto ayaṃ, bhagini, kāyo mānaṃ nissāya."
msgstr "‘This body is produced by conceit. Relying on conceit,"

msgctxt "an4.159:7.2"
msgid "Māno pahātabbo’ti, iti kho panetaṃ vuttaṃ."
msgstr "you should give up conceit.’ This is what I said,"

msgctxt "an4.159:7.3"
msgid "Kiñcetaṃ paṭicca vuttaṃ?"
msgstr "but why did I say it?"

msgctxt "an4.159:7.4"
msgid "Idha, bhagini, bhikkhu suṇāti:"
msgstr "Take a mendicant who hears this:"

msgctxt "an4.159:7.5"
msgid ""
"‘itthannāmo kira bhikkhu āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ "
"diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘They say that the mendicant named so-and-so has realized the undefiled "
"freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in this very life. And they live "
"having realized it with their own insight due to the ending of defilements.’"

msgctxt "an4.159:7.6"
msgid "Tassa evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "They think:"

msgctxt "an4.159:7.7"
msgid ""
"‘so hi nāma āyasmā āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ "
"diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharissati;"
msgstr ""
"‘Well, that venerable can realize the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom "
"by wisdom in this very life. …"

#. VAR: kimaṅgaṃ → kimaṅga (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.159:7.8"
msgid "kimaṅgaṃ panāhan’ti."
msgstr "Why can’t I?’"

msgctxt "an4.159:7.9"
msgid "So aparena samayena mānaṃ nissāya mānaṃ pajahati."
msgstr "After some time, relying on conceit, they give up conceit."

msgctxt "an4.159:7.10"
msgid "‘Mānasambhūto ayaṃ, bhagini, kāyo, mānaṃ nissāya māno pahātabbo’ti, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.159:7.11"
msgid "iti yaṃ taṃ vuttaṃ idametaṃ paṭicca vuttaṃ."
msgstr "That’s why I said what I said."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an4.159:8.1"
msgid "Methunasambhūto ayaṃ, bhagini, kāyo."
msgstr "‘This body is produced by sex."

msgctxt "an4.159:8.2"
msgid "Methune ca setughāto vutto bhagavatā”ti."
msgstr "The Buddha spoke of breaking off everything to do with sex.’”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an4.159:9.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho sā bhikkhunī mañcakā vuṭṭhahitvā ekaṃsaṃ uttarāsaṅgaṃ karitvā "
"āyasmato ānandassa pādesu sirasā nipatitvā āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then that nun rose from her cot, placed her robe over one shoulder, bowed "
"with her head at Ānanda’s feet, and said:"

msgctxt "an4.159:9.2"
msgid ""
"“accayo maṃ, bhante, accagamā, yathābālaṃ yathāmūḷhaṃ yathāakusalaṃ, yāhaṃ "
"evamakāsiṃ."
msgstr ""
"“I have made a mistake, sir. It was foolish, stupid, and unskillful of me to "
"act in that way."

msgctxt "an4.159:9.3"
msgid ""
"Tassā me, bhante, ayyo ānando accayaṃ accayato paṭiggaṇhātu, āyatiṃ "
"saṃvarāyā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Please, sir, accept my mistake for what it is, so I can restrain myself in "
"future.”"

#. VAR: Taggha taṃ → taggha tvaṃ (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an4.159:9.4"
msgid ""
"“Taggha taṃ, bhagini, accayo accagamā, yathābālaṃ yathāmūḷhaṃ yathāakusalaṃ, "
"yā tvaṃ evamakāsi."
msgstr ""
"“Indeed, sister, you made a mistake. It was foolish, stupid, and unskillful "
"of you to act in that way."

msgctxt "an4.159:9.5"
msgid ""
"Yato ca kho tvaṃ, bhagini, accayaṃ accayato disvā yathādhammaṃ paṭikarosi, "
"taṃ te mayaṃ paṭiggaṇhāma."
msgstr ""
"But since you have recognized your mistake for what it is, and have dealt "
"with it properly, I accept it."

msgctxt "an4.159:9.6"
msgid ""
"Vuddhi hesā, bhagini, ariyassa vinaye yo accayaṃ accayato disvā yathādhammaṃ "
"paṭikaroti āyatiṃ saṃvaraṃ āpajjatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"For it is growth in the training of the noble one to recognize a mistake for "
"what it is, deal with it properly, and commit to restraint in the future.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.159:9.7"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
